org.openrdf.rio

Interface RDFParserFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryRDFParserFactory, JSONLDParserFactory, N3ParserFactory, NQuadsParserFactory, NTriplesParserFactory, RDFJSONParserFactory, RDFXMLParserFactory, TriGParserFactory, TriXParserFactory, TurtleParserFactory

    public interface RDFParserFactory
    A RDFParserFactory returns RDFParsers for a specific RDF format.

    Arjohn Kampman
